description.narrative: The general objective of the Kingston Water and Sanitation Subprogram (hereinafter referred to as ¿Subprogram A¿) is to contribute to the improvement of the quality of life of the Kingston and St. Andrew population by improving the reliability of potable water supply and sanitation services. The specific objective is to initiate a program to improve the quality of the services provided to the Kingston and Saint Andrew Area and increase the efficiency and sustainability of the National Water Commission (¿NWC¿).¿
